  "body": "### Discussed in https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/discussions/4836\r\n\r\n<div type='discussions-op-text'>\r\n\r\n<sup>Originally posted by **aviaisenberg** March 10, 2022</sup>\r\nRan into an issue when writing automated deployment scripts that were different based on the network I was using. \r\n\r\nNoticed that when using dashboard, the network information is stored correct in the build files, but the network name is passed as dashboard to the migration script. \r\n\r\nIt would be really useful if the dashboard network would also convey which network it was connected to when being passed into the migration scripts. May even be more useful if the actual network appeared instead of network==\"dashboard\"\r\n\r\n</div>",
